Tim's Online Podcast

A modern and responsive podcast web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
This project allows users to listen to episodes, download audio files, and enjoy a premium, mobile-friendly interface.

Features
Audio Playback -> for each episode.
Download Button -> for instant audio file download.
Fully Responsive -> design for mobile, tablet, and desktop.
Premium UI/UX -> with smooth animations and hover effects.
Smooth Scroll Navigation and Active Link Highlighting.

---

Folder Structure
podcast-web-app/
│── index.html
│── README.md
│
├── css/
│ ├── style.css -> Main styling
│ └── responsive.css -> Mobile & tablet adjustments
│
├── js/
│ └── script.js -> Smooth scrolling & active nav
│
├── assets/
│ ├── audio/ -> Podcast episodes (MP3)
│ ├── images/ -> Episode covers & logos
│ └── icons/ -> SVG or PNG icons
│
└── data/
└── episodes.json -> Episode metadata (optional)


Future Improvements
Add search & filter for episodes.
Add playlist & favorites feature.
Implement upload feature with a backend.
Integrate with Spotify API or other podcast APIs.


